e="width: 1280px; height: 820px"><div class="iframe_placeholder" data-iframe="&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://v6p9d9t4.ssl.hwcdn.net/html/8173032/webgl/index.html&quot; allowtransparency=&quot;true&quot; webkitallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; mozallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; msallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; allow=&quot;autoplay; fullscreen *; geolocation; microphone; camera; midi; monetization; xr-spatial-tracking; gamepad; gyroscope; accelerometer; xr; cross-origin-isolated&quot; id=&quot;game_drop&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"><button class="button load_iframe_btn"><svg stroke-linejoin="round" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" role="img" stroke-width="2" class="svgicon icon_play" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden version="1.1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Run game</button></div></div></div><div class="donate"><a href="https://cattrigger.itch.io/melissa-heart/purchase" class="button donate_btn" data-donate="false">Download Now</a></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><h1 class="text-center"><br><a href="https://cattrigger.itch.io/date-time">Check out the Date Time❤️ Demo</a>&nbsp;- Featuring a Remake of Melissa❤️!</h1>  <p class="text-center"><em><br></em></p>  <p class="text-center"><em></em></p>  <p class="text-center"><em>~~Stay Updated on my latest projects!!~~</em>  </p>  <p class="text-center"><a href="https://www.tumblr.com/cattrigger" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Tumblr</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/cattrigger" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@cattrigger" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Tiktok</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2313010/Date_Time_Melissa_Morris_Anna/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Upcoming Big Project!</a>  </p>  <h1 class="text-center"><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2313010/Date_Time_Melissa_Morris_Anna/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Play the Trilogy Soon!</a></h1>  <p><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2313010/Date_Time_Melissa_Morris_Anna/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyMjk3ODI4LmpwZw==/original/UATX%2B9.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></p>  <p class="text-center"><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@cattrigger" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener"></a>  </p>  <p class="text-center"><br></p>  <p>Have you heard of this <strong>NEW GAME </strong>they installed on the high-tech computer at the library?&nbsp; We&#x27;ve all played it!&nbsp; <strong>You should too!&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>It&#x27;s real cute!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>  <p class="text-center"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEwMTUwNjg5LmdpZg==/original/wT7y3n.gif" loading="lazy"><br></p>  <p class="text-center">Meet&nbsp;<strong>MELISSA</strong>, your date in a brand spankin&#x27; new game called <strong>&quot;DATE TIME&quot;.</strong></p>  <p class="text-center">She is a sweetheart!&nbsp; A bright, young woman... who is looking for someone with a gentle touch!</p>  <p class="text-center">She loves a GOOD BOOK, and she has always wanted to date a TALENTED ARTIST!</p>  <p class="text-center">But she isn&#x27;t into SPORTS so JOCKS... please do NOT APPLY!</p>  <p class="text-center">Play your cards right, and you&#x27;ll get a SMOOCH from the cutest person ever!</p>  <p class="text-center"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEwMTUwNzg3LmdpZg==/original/%2FwVQbR.gif" loading="lazy"><br></p>  <p class="text-center"><br></p>  <p class="text-center">&quot;Melissa&nbsp;❤️&quot; is a <strong>short retro tech horror visual novel</strong>, with a bit of comedy that taps into the general time period of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apple_II_series" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">the Apple II</a>, and other examples of old computer tech.</p>  <p class="text-center">The game was done in under a week.</p>  <p class="text-center"><a href="https://emojipedia.org/red-heart/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener"><br></a><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEwMTUwNzQwLmdpZg==/original/LmiJoM.gif" loading="lazy"><br></p>  <p><a href="https://emojipedia.org/red-heart/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener"></a></p>  <p><br></p>  <p class="text-center"><strong>Content Warning:</strong></p>  <p class="text-center">-Flickering / Flashing lights</p>  <p class="text-center">-Strong Language</p>  <p class="text-center">-Appearance of blood</p>  <p class="text-center"><strong>-YOU WILL GET SMOOCHED</strong></p>  <p><em>Please ask for permission before redistributing&nbsp;this game in an official or altered form.&nbsp; If you would like the game to be translated in a different language, feel free to reach out to me.</em></p></div><div class="more_information_toggle"><div class="toggle_row"><a class="toggle_info_btn" href="javascript:void(0)">More information<svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_down_tick" height="6" width="12" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 37 20"><path d="m2.0858 0c-1.1535 0-2.0858 0.86469-2.0858 1.9331 0 0.5139 0.21354 1.0183 0.38704 1.1881l18.113 16.879 18.112-16.879c0.174-0.1696 0.388-0.674 0.388-1.1879 0-1.0684-0.932-1.9331-2.086-1.9331-0.577 0-1.111 0.23008-1.49 0.57992l-14.924 13.894-14.925-13.893c-0.3777-0.34998-0.9134-0.581-1.4902-0.581z"/></svg></a></div><div class="info_panel_wrapper"><div id="game_info_panel_4459626" class="game_info_panel_widget base_widget"><table><tbody><tr><td>Updated</td><td><abbr title="25 June 2023 @ 21:28"><span aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-stopwatch"></span> 4 days ago</abbr></td></tr><tr><td>Status</td><td><a href="https://itch.io/games/released">Released</a></td></tr><tr><td>Platforms</